=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dnhdennis\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d285ea80811c78ba4f2495a2b7b83bc0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d285ea80811c78ba4f2495a2b7b83bc0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dnhdennis\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dnhdennis</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 8, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had the Lets Encrypt certificate already working on the host server. This plugin was super easy to make sure that the site uses the SSL certificate.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Super simple</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hpemberton\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/969e2e1ca3abba9904af37fdf589041c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/969e2e1ca3abba9904af37fdf589041c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hpemberton\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hpemberton</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very simple to use - all set up in seconds. Works. No impact on performance. Free. So all in all I\'m very happy.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flowinglogic\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5ee735498cf4e3e0c19fd6af84b336fc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5ee735498cf4e3e0c19fd6af84b336fc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flowinglogic\" class=\"reviewer-name\">flowinglogic</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 14, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Definitely recommend this plugin! It worked exactly as advertised on the first try.\n\nWill be using on many of my sites, now. Much appreciated!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Above and Beyond with Help!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/douglas47\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b2ebac1a1aa80399f3fe06c218c2656?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b2ebac1a1aa80399f3fe06c218c2656?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/douglas47\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Douglas47</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Even though your plugin was working exactly the way it should, you went the extra mile and figured out my problem. Your responses were quick, professional, and extremely helpful.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thanks</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mgrosary\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aae6dacc60fd611be6ceab7bae7be67f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aae6dacc60fd611be6ceab7bae7be67f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mgrosary\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mgrosary</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 4, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This was super simple.  I had an ssl cert for a long time, but, knowing nothing, I couldn\'t figure out why it wasn\'t working!  It does now.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/facialflex\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ba98e6ff0e32065e045ccfb371fe9fdb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ba98e6ff0e32065e045ccfb371fe9fdb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/facialflex\" class=\"reviewer-name\">facialflex</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Having downloaded the plugin and found it hadnt solved my problem I contacted support. Manuel came back to me really quickly and helped me sort out the issue which was nothing to do with the plugin - it was an issue to do with my website but he still took the trouble to assist me.\n\nThanks Manuel.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zakandrawos\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caae93016b66c54f2c4f727ac9483c2e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caae93016b66c54f2c4f727ac9483c2e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zakandrawos\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zakandrawos</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Amazing plugin. worked with ease</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">AMAZING SUPPORT</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anabragasalgado\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/636f5ecd4aacb35179be28be52c44cc4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/636f5ecd4aacb35179be28be52c44cc4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anabragasalgado\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anabragasalgado</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin is amazing and simple! But I was having some troubles with mixed content .\n\nI was stressing out because but @manuelrocha88 Helped me so much and I was able to make it work thanks to him\"\n\nThe support sistem is really really good!\n\nAgain, thank you so much</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digitalew\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b2590c0bdbc3f430ce7320a455f9cac8?s=